origin.sil_yoni.guxi.name: 咕西
origin.sil_yoni.guxi.description: 兮芾的种族。看起来他们比较娇小，这是因为他们以能量组成了身体。由于是能量体，所以他们没有消化有机质的能力，但很明显他们不需要。他们无法抵御物理伤害，与此同时他们可以直接吸收热量。他们的眼睛与众不同。
origin.sil_yoni.fairy.name: Green Fairy
origin.sil_yoni.fairy.description: They are Treasures of the Forest. They often sprint in the air, but always stop because of their fragile bodies. They are also adept at interacting with nature.
origin.sil_yoni.fairy2.name: Void Fairy
origin.sil_yoni.fairy2.description: They are Treasures of the Forest. They often sprint in the air, but always stop because of their fragile bodies. They are also adept at interacting with nature.
origin.sil_yoni.silvigarabis.name: Silvigarabis
origin.sil_yoni.silvigarabis.description: 这是作者写给自己玩的种族。
power.sil_yoni.physique/fragile_body.des: 你身体虚弱，生命力下降，同时盔甲难以帮助你防御
power.sil_yoni.physique/weak_body.name: Weak Body
power.sil_yoni.physique/weak_body.descri: You have a weak body, which limits your ability to act.
power.sil_yoni.physique/weak_arms.name: Weak Arms
power.sil_yoni.physique/weak_arms.descri: Unless affected by Strength, mining speed is greatly decreased when breaking natural stone adjacent to 3 or more natural stones.
power.sil_yoni.physique/tiny_body.name: Tiny Treasure
power.sil_yoni.physique/tiny_body.descri: Your body is small, unlike ordinary humans, some things may be difficult for you to do, such as reaching further things, or jumping on a full block. But your attack speed will be faster.
power.sil_yoni.physique/small_body.name: 较小体型
power.sil_yoni.physique/small_body.descr: 你的身体比较小，类似于人类中的儿童。一些事情对你来说可能难以完成，比如够到更远的东西，又或者跳上一个完整的方块。
power.sil_yoni.forager.name: Master of Land Cultivation
power.sil_yoni.forager.description: Cultivating in nature makes you understand how to get higher yields from crops
power.sil_yoni.bee_rider.name: Bee rider
power.sil_yoni.bee_rider.description: Bees are willing to be your mounts! As long as you don't hurt them......
power.sil_yoni.glowing_vision.name: Bright Vision
power.sil_yoni.glowing_vision.descriptio: While making yourself glow, you can also see everything around you clearly (immune to darkness effect and gain glowing effect and night vision effect when using ability).
power.sil_yoni.firefly_lighter.name: 萤火虫发光体
power.sil_yoni.firefly_lighter.descripti: 当你处于空中时，你的身体会发光
power.sil_yoni.glow_lighter.name: Glow
power.sil_yoni.forest_s_giving.name: Forest Blessing
power.sil_yoni.forest_s_giving.descripti: When you are in the forest, your attributes are slightly improved, and you can recover life quickly.
power.sil_yoni.sun_s_helping.name: 日光的帮助
power.sil_yoni.sun_s_helping.description: 处于阳光中，你的各项属性小幅提高，并且可以缓慢恢复生命。
power.sil_yoni.fluttering_wings.name: Magic Wings
power.sil_yoni.fluttering_wings.descript: You have magical wings that can take you to the sky.
power.sil_yoni.void_space.name: 进入到虚空的能力
power.sil_yoni.void_space.cooldown_deny_: 由于传送通道尚不稳定，无法切换空间。
power.sil_yoni.void_space.live_keep: 你在虚空空间里死亡了，被迫从中出来。
power.sil_yoni.fairy/fairy_wings.name: Fairy Wings
power.sil_yoni.fairy/fairy_wings.descrip: You can fly! But not for too long, because that might hurt your body. Wearing heavy armor will also increase your stamina consumption when flying.
power.sil_yoni.fairy/heal_magic.name: Healing Magic
power.sil_yoni.fairy/heal_magic.descript: Bring your healing magic to those around you and increase your own temporary protection!
power.sil_yoni.fairy/fairy_physique.name: Fairy Physique
power.sil_yoni.fairy/fairy_physique.desc: Fairies have a special secret to keep themselves energetic!
death.attack.guxi_starve_energy.player: %1$s在与%2$s战斗时没能保持能量充足
sil_yoni.gui.badge.long_press_active_in_: 在虚空空间当中长按 %s 使用
